lyrics:
[verse]
My friends and I, we gather round
Friday nights at my place, spells abound
But this week, they all have plans
Leaving me to face magic's lands

[chorus]
My friends can't play Magic the Gathering with me
Their absence leaves an emptiness, can't you see
I hold my cards, waiting for the game to start
But it seems this Friday night, I'll play alone, my heart apart
